snippet.title: Nazo Puyo, Game Gear Playthrough Part 1 | Levels 1-33
snippet.description:
Don't worry, my playthrough for Nazo Puyo for the PC-98 is not dead. I'm starting over with that one, I am still studying Japanese.

As for now, I'm going to do a different playthrough, with the original Nazo Puyo. Nazo Puyo is a mission based spin-off of Puyo Puyo, released in 1993. There really isn't much to say about the game but you have 99 levels, which you can revisit at anytime and you can make your own puzzles too.

The game is my channel's first officially recorded Sega Game Gear playthough, not from a test recording. The footage was recorded from a real game cartridge with the Analogue Mega SG & recorded via ElGato HD60S.

#PuyoPuyo #NazoPuyo #GameGear
